 for tax it also provides lending products such as loans by bill loans on deed and overdrafts and discounts for bills and bank acceptances commercial papers and documentary bills in addition the company is involved in buying and selling securities and government bonds investment in government bonds corporate bonds stocks and other securities for deposit payout reserve and fund management and provision of exchange for remittance credit to current accounts and money collection services further it provides various foreign exchange services related to imports exports and foreign remittance corporate bond trustee and management trustee services and agency services for public bond subscriptions register of public bonds etc additionally the company acts as a receiving agent for payment for shares as well as paying agent for stock dividends and public bond principals and interests an agent for the organization workers retirement allowance mutual aid etc and provides agency loans on behalf of public sector financial institutions it also offers safekeeping and safe deposit securities lending debt guarantee public bond underwriting lottery trust agent consulting and pension administrative services sells securities investment trusts buys and sells gold handles commercial papers sells insurance policies and provides interest rate and currency derivatives and other derivatives the company was founded in  and is headquartered in tokyo japan detailed description  marunouchichiyodakutokyo  japanfounded in  employees phone     wwwmizuhobankcom key executives for mizuho bank ltd mizuho bank ltd does not have any key executives recorded mizuho bank ltd key developments mizuho bank presents at asifma structured finance conference  sep  am sep   mizuho bank presents at asifma structured finance conference  sep  am venue clifford chance singapore office marina bay financial centre th floor tower   marina boulevard singapore  singapore speakers hiroyuki kasama structured finance division m