en the former mizuho bank and the former mizuho corporate bank took place and the institution was named mizuho bank servicesedit current accounts cash cards for use in japan only international cash cards international money transfers credit cards saving accounts loans internet banking website all services including internet banking and the main website are in japanese only some branches hire englishspeaking employees all services except for international cash cards credit cards and international money transfers are limited within the territory of japan restrictions on foreign nationals apply particularly loans are available only for japanese nationals and permanent residents of japan holding permanent employmentcitation needed botched trading scandal of edit on thursday december   shares of recruitment firm jcom debuted at  japanese yen ¥  on the tokyo stock exchange the tse an inexperienced trader at mizuho intending to sell one share at ¥ instead sent an order at  am to the tse to sell  shares of jcom at ¥ each essentially attempting to sell  billion worth of stock for only  in addition the size of mizuhos sell order was  times the total number of jcom shares see alsoedit mizuho financial group mizuho corporate bank referencesedit  httpwwwmizuhobankcomcompanyreleasecbindexhtml  httpwwwmizuhobankcomcompanyreleasecbpdfnewspdf  httpwwwmizuhofgcojpenglishcompanyinfopdfreleaseengpdf  httpwwwmizuhofgcojpenglishreleasereleaseenghtml  operational risk  regulation  welcome to operational risk  regulation risknet external linksedit mizuho bank in japanese mizuho bank mizuho financial group the japan times – tse wont let mizuho duck jcom fiasco december   risknet – blame spreads over mizuho trading error december   msnbccom – botched stock trade costs japan firm m – december   risknet – mizuho securities loses m in trading error january   tokyo stock exchange – board report – april  the japan times – tse to blame for trading error court – december   the japan times – mizuho 